en_831997_0	Hon Minister of Small & Medium Business and Enterprise Development, Industries and Supply Chain Management, Hon Wimal Weerawansa (MP), along with the Secretary to the Ministry Mr. J.A Ranjith and several other officials during a tour to the north visited the Security Force Headquarters - Jaffna (SFHQ-J) on Friday (17).
en_831997_1	Major General Ruwan Wanigasooriya, Commander, Security Forces - Jaffna welcomed the ministerial delegation and presented them with a detailed briefing on the current status quo and the role and tasks of the Security Forces in Jaffna.
en_831997_2	Few senior officers also were at the venue, including the General Officer Commanding, 51 Division during the meeting.
en_831997_3	Meanwhile, Major General Ruwan Wanigasooriya, Commander, Security Forces -Jaffna on Friday (17) paid a courtesy call on the newly-appointed Northern Province Governor, Mrs P.S.M Charles at her office in Jaffna.
en_831997_4	During the courtesy meeting, both of them discussed matters of relevance to the welfare of Jaffna civilians and projects, being pursued by the troops in Jaffna.
